repair.repairedDockerfile:
# see https://docs.docker.com/docker-cloud/builds/advanced/
# using ARG in FROM requires min v17.05.0-ce
ARG QGIS_DOCKER_TAG=latest

FROM  qgis/qgis:${QGIS_DOCKER_TAG}
MAINTAINER Denis Rouzaud <denis@opengis.ch>

RUN curl -L -f https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py | python3

WORKDIR /root

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade sphinx-rtd-theme numpydoc

RUN mkdir /root/pyqgis
COPY . /root/pyqgis
WORKDIR /root/pyqgis

CMD /bin/bash -c "/root/pyqgis/scripts/build-docs.sh -v ${QGIS_VERSION} ${BUILD_OPTIONS}"
